text: The Yakima Valley Subdivision is a railway line in southern Washington running about Pasco, Washington to Ellensburg, Washington.Map of BNSF Northern Division It is operated by BNSF Railway and is considered part of the Northern Transcon. == References == ==External links== *BNSF Subdivisions Category:BNSF Railway lines Category:Rail infrastructure in Washington (state)
title: Yakima Valley Subdivision
